            "_comment": "Regression test: HD-elevated symbol layer that is icon-only and line-placed (`symbol-elevation-reference: hd-road-markup` + `symbol-placement: line` + `icon-image` with no `text-field`). This combination used to trip `assert(index >= 0)` in SymbolInstanceArray.get because `SymbolHDExtension.getElevationFeatureForPlacedSymbol` (formerly `getElevationFeatureForText`) indexed the bucket's empty text buffer regardless of which buffer the caller was iterating.",
